title: Event LIVE Creator showdown
description:
Rules

One and done LIVE Matches
Scheduled LIVE Matches are one and done.
Your opponent must arrive within 15 minutes, or they will be disqualified automatically.
Please refrain from making rude comments or engaging in hateful behavior during the match.
Do not threaten or harass your opponent before the LIVE Match, its for fun
Other Creator Network Members are not required to show up
It is a fun bonding activity to earn more diamonds & meet other agency members!
No shows will not be able to participate next time.
Make an event by: Going to your Profile > Settings > Settings and Privacy > LIVE > LIVE Events > Create event
Let your Team know ahead of time.
We have the right to post/share your contact information with the scheduled match so you can contact your opponent and vise versa before the LIVE match

Results will be communicated by Tuesday 6:00PM PST TIME The following week

Report your score: https://forms.gle/HUCTrbmxZE3UGVL1A

IF YOUR OPPONENT DOES NOT SHOW UP REPORT IT HERE, DO NOT CONTACT YOUR MANAGER
NO Show Report form: https://forms.gle/zsEWvC8F2SvjcxzBA

Creator with the highest score each week gets 10,000 Diamonds (Must make a min of 50,000 diamonds in the match to be eligible for the payout)

If you put in a quit request you will be ineligible to participate in events including LIVE Creator Showdown.

If your opponent does not show fill out this form: https://forms.gle/mDjpRWhfwxhM9seTA (Do not spam discord or your agent)

SIGN UP FORM: https://forms.gle/Rt9ZEJNn7Ng5UnkF6
